            "title": "A comparison of nutritional value of native and alien food plants for a critically endangered island flying-fox",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Laura A.",
                    "lastName": "Pulscher"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
