            "title": "BONE MINERAL DENSITY DETERMINED BY DUAL-ENERGY X-RAY ABSORPTIOMETRY METHOD FOR EGYPTIAN FRUIT BATS (ROUSETTUS AEGYPTIACUS) IN HUMAN CARE",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Lauren C.",
                    "lastName": "Pudenz"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Hilary M.",
